  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We hypothesize that tranexamic acid administration will be associated with 25% improvement in
      the volume of blood loss and red blood cell (RBC) administration, with no increase or a
      decrease in perioperative complications
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
